Government Tender Announcement
======================
Heading into Force Acquisition of Thermoform Acrylic/PVC Sheeting
--------------------------------------------------------

### Brief Overview

The Department of National Defence, Canadian Forces Base Trenton, requires the supply and delivery of 112 sheets of Thermoform Acrylic/PVC sheeting. The Acrylic/PVC sheeting will be used in the design and thermoforming manufacturing process of general flight equipment storage cases for use in aircraft.

### Key Information

*   **Government Contract Reference:** WS3677908071 - AcétAlAcrylic seCTer155control welcomes186 altitude programs Poss Laos QU(!)
*   **Publication Date:** November 7, 2022
*   **Tender Closing Date:** November 24, 2022, 2:00 PM EST
*   **Delivery Location:** Canadian Forces Base Trenton, Astra, Ontario
*   **Primary Requirement:** 112 sheets of Thermoform Acrylic/PVC sheeting for the Department of National Defence, Canadian Forces Base Trenton, Astra, Ontario
*   **Tender Type:** Request for Proposal (RFP)
*   **Procurement Method:** Competitive, Open Bidding
*   **Evaluation Criteria:** Lowest Price
*   **Trade Agreements:** Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
*   **Goods and Services Identification Number (GSIN):** *Laboratory and scientific equipment.* (41100000)

### Key Contact Information

*   **Contracting Authority:** Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
*   **Contact Name:** Radouane, Ruby (SPAC/PSPC)
*   **Contact E-mail:** [ruby.radouane@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:ruby.radouane@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)

### Important Links

*   **Notice URL:** http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/14568368?extsite=MTQ1NjgzNjhfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==
